ygData.messageBody:
The Mystic alliance (www.mysticalliance.com) does indeed exist, and there
are around 60 members (about 40 of which are semi to fully active). I fall
into the inactive category. (on a hiatus for various reasons, not the least
of which is Anarchy Online) We are on the Rodcet NIfe server, and the web
page should give you an idea of us. (There's a fine, active message board
there). As far as officers, they'd be Snapdragyn, Ompa, Taren, Gwynap,
Gunarr, Aethyra, Trinic, Marri, Gaiwan, Vargyr, Andelyve, Gaybriel, Leta, or
Armande (if I'm on...still have some time left on the current pay
period...stop in now and then to say hi). If I left out any officers, I'm
sorry. Anyone else in the guild would be happy to talk to ya, but those are
the people who can do the inviting. :-) So we're not by any means dead.

Peas,
Rob
Armande V'lu
